<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4361ee, #7209b7);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .loader {
            border: 5px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            border-radius: 50%;
            border-top: 5px solid white;
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
            margin: 30px auto;
        }
        @keyframes spin {
            0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Redirection vers la page de paiement</h1>
    <p>Veuillez patienter, vous allez être redirigé vers la page de paiement sécurisée...</p>
    <div class="loader"></div>
    
    <!-- Formulaire caché qui sera soumis automatiquement -->
    <form id="paymentForm" method="POST" action="https://tikespam.com/collection/create" style="display: none;">
        <input type="text" name="item_name" value="<%= item_name %>">
        <input type="number" name="amount" value="<%= amount %>">
        <input type="email" name="email" value="<%= email %>">
        <input type="text" name="phone" value="<%= phone %>">
        <input type="text" name="client_name" value="<%= client_name %>">
        <input type="url" name="success_url" value="<%= success_url %>">
        <input type="url" name="failed_url" value="<%= failed_url %>">
        <input type="text" name="api_key" value="<%= api_key %>">
    </form>
    
    <script>
        // Soumettre le formulaire automatiquement après chargement de la page
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
            setTimeout(function() {
                document.getElementById('paymentForm').submit();
            }, 1500); // Délai de 1.5 secondes pour montrer l'animation de chargement
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html> 